@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wahmuz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.63 / ((v2 + 0.59 - tmp + 0.01) + (v2 + 0.01 + tmp + 0.91)))
    v2 = 0.54
    tmp = (0.82 + wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.87)))
    v0 = ((0.17 - wp.abs(v1 + 0.06)) + ((tmp + 0.90 + v0 + 0.57) / v0))
    data[tid] = v0
